strings: <voice_0x01000E15><se_def>Legal!: I have often seen the passing of the moon, but never felt what time it is.
<voice_0x01000E16><se_def>Legal!: Get search results instantly. I found the Lunar Harp.
<voice_0x01000E17><se_def>Legal!: Show off your amazing engine that brings back memories of the sea.
<voice_0x01000E19><se_def>Legal!: I don't believe I will ever touch her. Now let's concentrate on the task at hand.
<voice_0x01000E1A><se_def>Legal!: Let's go boat. Music wakes me up again.
